data.description: Welcome to your new oasis! This lovely all-brick ranch home comes with a private gunite pool, detached in-law suite complete with kitchen and full bathroom, and a 12x18 workshop that houses tools, lawn equipment, and the pool equipment. The main home is over 2200 sq ft and boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a massive great room, a secondary living room, a breakfast room complete with a coffee bar and floor to ceiling cabinets, and a utility room off the great room perfect for an office or a craft room. The kitchen comes with a drop-in, single basin sink and flawless vinyl countertops. The in-law suite adds another 700+ sq ft of living space and comes complete with a living room, bedroom, breakfast room, kitchen, laundry room, and full bathroom. The in-law suite is perfect for grown-up children, your in-laws, or rent it out for additional income! Sellers want your purchase to be worry-free, so they are offering a 1-year home warranty with an acceptable offer. This home offers everything one could want and won't last long, so call Shane or Rose Marie to schedule your private showing today!
